commit.message: Add support for building functables out-of-directory

Fix test directory

Reported by OBATA Akio. Thanks!!!

set MAXPATHLEN as 1024

GNU Hurd doesn't have MAXPATHLEN

Some architectures has stub for getcontext, so we just use CHECK_FUNCS

Author: NIIBE Yutaka <gniibe@fsij.org>

Use COMPILER_LOG instead of TESTS_ENVIRONMENT for test runner

Using TESTS_ENVIRONMENT for specifying test runner is deprecated.

See also:
https://www.gnu.org/software/automake/manual/html_node/Serial-Test-Harness.html#Serial-Test-Harness
